This is the clapper_plus-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the clapper_plus blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'clapper_plus', which is imported as:

    import clapper_plus

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(clapper_plus)
